WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.800 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:02.920 align:middle line:84%
>> Judith Orloff
walks in two worlds.

00:00:02.920 --> 00:00:06.400 align:middle line:84%
She's a psychiatrist who has
melded her practice in medicine

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:09.280 align:middle line:84%
with her work in the fields
of energy and intuition.

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:11.110 align:middle line:84%
The combination of
these two skills

00:00:11.110 --> 00:00:12.970 align:middle line:84%
allows her to take
her clients deep

00:00:12.970 --> 00:00:16.000 align:middle line:84%
into their own transformation
and healing process.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.640 align:middle line:84%
As the author of books such as
"Second Sight" and "Positive

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:22.240 align:middle line:84%
Energy," Judith has been able
to help thousands understand

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:25.780 align:middle line:84%
why life can be such a drain
on our energies and emotions.

00:00:25.780 --> 00:00:27.550 align:middle line:84%
She says for many
of us it has to do

00:00:27.550 --> 00:00:30.800 align:middle line:84%
with being overly empathic and
intuitive, and not knowing it.

00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:40.430 align:middle line:90%


00:00:40.430 --> 00:00:42.140 align:middle line:84%
You've had an
interesting experience

00:00:42.140 --> 00:00:44.540 align:middle line:90%
occur at a tender age.

00:00:44.540 --> 00:00:46.850 align:middle line:84%
Can you talk about it,
and how it started shaping

00:00:46.850 --> 00:00:48.395 align:middle line:90%
future events in your life?

00:00:48.395 --> 00:00:51.140 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, now I'm a psychiatrist,
and I work a lot with

00:00:51.140 --> 00:00:53.120 align:middle line:84%
intuition, but
when I was a child,

00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:55.940 align:middle line:84%
I would have all these intuitive
experiences that would happen

00:00:55.940 --> 00:00:59.010 align:middle line:84%
that would scare me
a tremendous amount.

00:00:59.010 --> 00:01:00.920 align:middle line:84%
And my parents were
both physicians,

00:01:00.920 --> 00:01:03.850 align:middle line:84%
and I have 25
physicians in my family.

00:01:03.850 --> 00:01:07.520 align:middle line:84%
And so I have all of this
logical, linear, rational

00:01:07.520 --> 00:01:10.760 align:middle line:84%
family, and I was a little
girl who would predict things.

00:01:10.760 --> 00:01:12.680 align:middle line:84%
I would know if
someone was going

00:01:12.680 --> 00:01:14.830 align:middle line:84%
to die, if someone was
going to get a divorce,

00:01:14.830 --> 00:01:18.310 align:middle line:84%
if they were sick, if
someone was untrustworthy.

00:01:18.310 --> 00:01:21.710 align:middle line:84%
And I finally had an
experience with my mother,

00:01:21.710 --> 00:01:24.490 align:middle line:84%
where I had a dream
about her mentor

00:01:24.490 --> 00:01:26.490 align:middle line:84%
who was running for a
judgeship in Philadelphia.

00:01:26.490 --> 00:01:28.160 align:middle line:10%
Not only did he
lose the election,

00:01:28.160 --> 00:01:31.760 align:middle line:10%
but someone in the dream ran
up to him and bit his hand

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:33.470 align:middle line:10%
and really injured him.

00:01:33.470 --> 00:01:35.670 align:middle line:84%
And I told my mother about
this, and she said, oh,

00:01:35.670 --> 00:01:37.503 align:middle line:84%
why do you keep saying
these negative things

00:01:37.503 --> 00:01:39.350 align:middle line:90%
about my friends.

00:01:39.350 --> 00:01:41.190 align:middle line:90%
And I felt horrible of course.

00:01:41.190 --> 00:01:44.300 align:middle line:84%
And it turned out the election
night he did lose the election,

00:01:44.300 --> 00:01:46.340 align:middle line:84%
and his daughter-in-law
had a psychotic break

00:01:46.340 --> 00:01:49.020 align:middle line:84%
and ran up and bit his
hand at the polling place,

00:01:49.020 --> 00:01:51.720 align:middle line:84%
and was taken away to
a psychiatric hospital.

00:01:51.720 --> 00:01:54.050 align:middle line:84%
And so at that point
my mother forbade me

00:01:54.050 --> 00:01:57.290 align:middle line:84%
to ever mention any of my
intuitions at home again,

00:01:57.290 --> 00:01:58.790 align:middle line:84%
and I grew up
believing that there

00:01:58.790 --> 00:02:00.350 align:middle line:90%
was something wrong with me.

00:02:00.350 --> 00:02:02.780 align:middle line:84%
That I was somehow knowing
about these things,

00:02:02.780 --> 00:02:06.350 align:middle line:84%
but I was causing them, at the
same time, which is not true.

00:02:06.350 --> 00:02:07.740 align:middle line:90%
Which is not true.

00:02:07.740 --> 00:02:10.340 align:middle line:84%
And so I went
through a long period

00:02:10.340 --> 00:02:12.800 align:middle line:84%
of running from my
intuitions and feeling

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:15.260 align:middle line:84%
that I wanted to escape it,
and I got very heavily involved

00:02:15.260 --> 00:02:18.470 align:middle line:84%
with drugs in the 60's
trying to numb myself out.

00:02:18.470 --> 00:02:20.945 align:middle line:84%
I didn't want to
feel your energy.

00:02:20.945 --> 00:02:22.820 align:middle line:84%
I didn't want to know
what was inside of you.

00:02:22.820 --> 00:02:24.410 align:middle line:90%
I didn't want to know anything.

00:02:24.410 --> 00:02:26.640 align:middle line:90%
I didn't want that sensitivity.

00:02:26.640 --> 00:02:29.240 align:middle line:84%
And then I had an
experience, around that time,

00:02:29.240 --> 00:02:32.030 align:middle line:84%
where I went over
a cliff in a car

00:02:32.030 --> 00:02:34.200 align:middle line:90%
one night, where I was partying.

00:02:34.200 --> 00:02:37.370 align:middle line:84%
I was out and I met this guy,
and we went up to Tuna Canyon--

00:02:37.370 --> 00:02:39.096 align:middle line:90%
which is up near Malibu Canyon--

00:02:39.096 --> 00:02:40.220 align:middle line:90%
in the middle of the night.

00:02:40.220 --> 00:02:41.694 align:middle line:84%
We were talking,
and then the car--

00:02:41.694 --> 00:02:43.110 align:middle line:84%
we were not paying
much attention,

00:02:43.110 --> 00:02:45.800 align:middle line:90%
and the car went over the cliff.

00:02:45.800 --> 00:02:48.350 align:middle line:84%
And as we were turning--
we went over eight times,

00:02:48.350 --> 00:02:49.670 align:middle line:90%
I remember counting--

00:02:49.670 --> 00:02:53.270 align:middle line:84%
I got catapulted to this
tunnel, where everything

00:02:53.270 --> 00:02:56.120 align:middle line:84%
was amazingly quiet
and blue green,

00:02:56.120 --> 00:03:00.110 align:middle line:84%
and just atoms whirling
at enormous speeds.

00:03:00.110 --> 00:03:02.000 align:middle line:84%
And I was in this
very quiet place

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:04.790 align:middle line:84%
as the car was going
over, and we landed.

00:03:04.790 --> 00:03:06.650 align:middle line:84%
Then I came back
from that place,

00:03:06.650 --> 00:03:09.650 align:middle line:90%
and I was unharmed, as he was.

00:03:09.650 --> 00:03:14.570 align:middle line:10%
So we climbed up the cliff,
and we went our separate ways.

00:03:14.570 --> 00:03:16.700 align:middle line:84%
It was the only time
I ever met this man.

00:03:16.700 --> 00:03:17.500 align:middle line:90%
Just--

00:03:17.500 --> 00:03:18.980 align:middle line:90%
>> Amazing you went through--

00:03:18.980 --> 00:03:20.970 align:middle line:90%
was he driving?

00:03:20.970 --> 00:03:22.154 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, he was.

00:03:22.154 --> 00:03:24.320 align:middle line:84%
>> So he just took you into
this experience, really?

00:03:24.320 --> 00:03:26.960 align:middle line:84%
>> Yes, we met that night,
we had the experience,

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:29.696 align:middle line:84%
and then we left and
I never saw him again.

00:03:29.696 --> 00:03:31.820 align:middle line:84%
So we were just meant to
go through that experience

00:03:31.820 --> 00:03:32.620 align:middle line:90%
together.

00:03:32.620 --> 00:03:34.220 align:middle line:84%
But after that
experience, my parents

00:03:34.220 --> 00:03:35.990 align:middle line:84%
forced me to go
see a psychiatrist,

00:03:35.990 --> 00:03:38.450 align:middle line:84%
because they were so afraid
I was harming myself,

00:03:38.450 --> 00:03:39.980 align:middle line:90%
which I was.

00:03:39.980 --> 00:03:42.110 align:middle line:84%
And he-- the
psychiatrist that they

00:03:42.110 --> 00:03:44.030 align:middle line:84%
sent me to was the
first man who really

00:03:44.030 --> 00:03:47.090 align:middle line:84%
helped me to learn
about my intuitions,

00:03:47.090 --> 00:03:49.520 align:middle line:84%
and realized that I had
to embrace them in order

00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:51.200 align:middle line:90%
to be whole and healthy.

00:03:51.200 --> 00:03:55.410 align:middle line:84%
So I began working through the
shame of having this ability.

00:03:55.410 --> 00:03:59.660 align:middle line:84%
And he got me started on
opening up to intuition,

00:03:59.660 --> 00:04:01.365 align:middle line:84%
and sent me over
to Thelma Moss, who

00:04:01.365 --> 00:04:04.100 align:middle line:84%
was a parapsychology
researcher at UCLA.

00:04:04.100 --> 00:04:07.520 align:middle line:84%
And while I was at Thelma's lab
working there as a volunteer,

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:10.010 align:middle line:84%
I had a dream in which
a voice came to me

00:04:10.010 --> 00:04:13.070 align:middle line:84%
and told me to-- that I
was going to get an MD

00:04:13.070 --> 00:04:16.160 align:middle line:84%
and become a psychiatrist
to help legitimize intuition

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:18.470 align:middle line:90%
and medicine, very, very clear.

00:04:18.470 --> 00:04:21.360 align:middle line:84%
And I woke up in the
morning and I had--

00:04:21.360 --> 00:04:22.320 align:middle line:90%
totally surprised.

00:04:22.320 --> 00:04:25.010 align:middle line:84%
I had no desire, conscious
desire, to do that.

00:04:25.010 --> 00:04:28.280 align:middle line:84%
I was more artistic, and living
in Venice Beach with my artist

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:29.450 align:middle line:90%
boyfriend.

00:04:29.450 --> 00:04:31.790 align:middle line:84%
But because I was beginning
to trust my intuition,

00:04:31.790 --> 00:04:34.370 align:middle line:84%
I went and enrolled
at a junior college.

00:04:34.370 --> 00:04:37.400 align:middle line:84%
I'd been out of school, and
then one course became two,

00:04:37.400 --> 00:04:40.280 align:middle line:84%
became 14 years of
medical training.

00:04:40.280 --> 00:04:43.160 align:middle line:84%
>> How did that work for you,
going through the traditional

00:04:43.160 --> 00:04:46.790 align:middle line:84%
methodologies and
the root of medicine,

00:04:46.790 --> 00:04:49.340 align:middle line:84%
knowing what you already knew
and what you were going to be

00:04:49.340 --> 00:04:50.450 align:middle line:90%
bringing to it later?

00:04:50.450 --> 00:04:52.820 align:middle line:84%
It sounds like it took a lot
of patience and diligence

00:04:52.820 --> 00:04:54.359 align:middle line:90%
on your part to go through this.

00:04:54.359 --> 00:04:56.150 align:middle line:84%
Although you do have
a historical precedent

00:04:56.150 --> 00:04:57.485 align:middle line:90%
in your family for it.

00:04:57.485 --> 00:05:01.170 align:middle line:84%
>> I do, but I had to learn
how to really exercise my left

00:05:01.170 --> 00:05:01.970 align:middle line:90%
brain.

00:05:01.970 --> 00:05:03.830 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know how
to learn science.

00:05:03.830 --> 00:05:07.740 align:middle line:84%
I was very artistic, and I never
learned how to really do that.

00:05:07.740 --> 00:05:09.710 align:middle line:84%
And so I had to learn,
and I had many angels

00:05:09.710 --> 00:05:12.140 align:middle line:84%
who came in my path
to help me to do that,

00:05:12.140 --> 00:05:13.820 align:middle line:90%
because I needed help.

00:05:13.820 --> 00:05:15.950 align:middle line:84%
And I developed
a deep, deep love

00:05:15.950 --> 00:05:17.810 align:middle line:84%
for medicine and
the human body as I

00:05:17.810 --> 00:05:19.550 align:middle line:90%
was going through my training.

00:05:19.550 --> 00:05:21.810 align:middle line:90%
And what was just really--

00:05:21.810 --> 00:05:25.280 align:middle line:84%
you know, I fell in love when I
first started seeing patients,

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:27.140 align:middle line:84%
because I got to
sit by the bedside

00:05:27.140 --> 00:05:29.270 align:middle line:84%
and listen to patients
tell their stories,

00:05:29.270 --> 00:05:31.680 align:middle line:90%
and it was-- it for me.

00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:32.860 align:middle line:90%
I always loved it.

00:05:32.860 --> 00:05:36.860 align:middle line:84%
I still-- it is what makes being
a physician so powerful for me.

00:05:36.860 --> 00:05:39.230 align:middle line:84%
And so I combine
traditional medicine.

00:05:39.230 --> 00:05:41.700 align:middle line:84%
I have a deep love for what I
learned in my medical school

00:05:41.700 --> 00:05:43.320 align:middle line:90%
training about the body.

00:05:43.320 --> 00:05:48.240 align:middle line:84%
I was in surgeries seeing
the body exposed and holding

00:05:48.240 --> 00:05:51.000 align:middle line:84%
organs in my hand, and
seeing a heart pumping,

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:53.910 align:middle line:84%
and holding the GI tract
in my hand, and the uterus,

00:05:53.910 --> 00:05:55.270 align:middle line:90%
and kidneys.

00:05:55.270 --> 00:05:59.040 align:middle line:84%
And I saw everything, and
certainly from my intuition,

00:05:59.040 --> 00:06:01.320 align:middle line:84%
touching these organs
really helped me,

00:06:01.320 --> 00:06:03.107 align:middle line:90%
because I remember things.

00:06:03.107 --> 00:06:04.940 align:middle line:84%
And you have the sense
memory in your hands,

00:06:04.940 --> 00:06:07.380 align:middle line:84%
and so, as working
with intuition,

00:06:07.380 --> 00:06:09.630 align:middle line:84%
that helps me tremendously
now because I remember.

00:06:09.630 --> 00:06:11.010 align:middle line:90%
I know the vibe of the body.

00:06:11.010 --> 00:06:12.930 align:middle line:90%
I know the energy in the body.

00:06:12.930 --> 00:06:17.730 align:middle line:84%
And so I continue to have a
deep love for medicine now,

00:06:17.730 --> 00:06:20.340 align:middle line:84%
and so I combine traditional
medicine with intuition.

00:06:20.340 --> 00:06:21.850 align:middle line:90%
I don't have a preference.

00:06:21.850 --> 00:06:22.650 align:middle line:90%
I don't.

00:06:22.650 --> 00:06:26.130 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I see them
as being interwoven.

00:06:26.130 --> 00:06:29.190 align:middle line:84%
And I just use the best
from traditional medicine

00:06:29.190 --> 00:06:31.950 align:middle line:84%
and also intuition,
spirituality, subtle energies

00:06:31.950 --> 00:06:33.240 align:middle line:90%
to help my patients.

00:06:33.240 --> 00:06:35.650 align:middle line:90%
Whatever will help, I will do.

00:06:35.650 --> 00:06:37.010 align:middle line:90%
I don't have any bias.

00:06:37.010 --> 00:06:38.520 align:middle line:90%
>> So when someone--

00:06:38.520 --> 00:06:41.310 align:middle line:84%
when you first started
taking clients--

00:06:41.310 --> 00:06:43.650 align:middle line:84%
or patients, started
seeing patients,

00:06:43.650 --> 00:06:46.560 align:middle line:84%
did you immediately kick
in to the blend of both

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:47.400 align:middle line:90%
of your skills?

00:06:47.400 --> 00:06:49.740 align:middle line:84%
Or did you have to follow
protocols rather strictly,

00:06:49.740 --> 00:06:51.150 align:middle line:84%
because you were
new at the game?

00:06:51.150 --> 00:06:53.752 align:middle line:84%
Or how did this start
blossoming for you

00:06:53.752 --> 00:06:55.460 align:middle line:84%
in the beginning toward
what it is today?

00:06:55.460 --> 00:06:56.610 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, I wrote--

00:06:56.610 --> 00:06:59.280 align:middle line:84%
this is my journey I wrote my
first book, "Second Sight,"

00:06:59.280 --> 00:07:02.130 align:middle line:84%
and I really chronicled
everything that I went through.

00:07:02.130 --> 00:07:04.740 align:middle line:84%
But what was so
interesting is that, when

00:07:04.740 --> 00:07:08.190 align:middle line:84%
I went into medical
school, I strayed very far

00:07:08.190 --> 00:07:09.900 align:middle line:84%
from the intuitive
realm, and I went

00:07:09.900 --> 00:07:12.740 align:middle line:84%
the exact opposite
direction for 12 years.

00:07:12.740 --> 00:07:15.540 align:middle line:84%
I would see patients come
in, rolling in on gurneys,

00:07:15.540 --> 00:07:17.140 align:middle line:90%
claiming to be psychic.

00:07:17.140 --> 00:07:21.720 align:middle line:84%
And tied down, with the police
there, and saying, I'm psychic,

00:07:21.720 --> 00:07:24.510 align:middle line:84%
I'm hearing the voice of God
and the FBI is out to get me,

00:07:24.510 --> 00:07:25.950 align:middle line:90%
and my food is poisoned.

00:07:25.950 --> 00:07:28.620 align:middle line:84%
And so we would take these
psychotic patients up

00:07:28.620 --> 00:07:30.780 align:middle line:84%
to the inpatient wards
and medicate them

00:07:30.780 --> 00:07:33.180 align:middle line:84%
with Haldol, Thorazine,
and they would no longer

00:07:33.180 --> 00:07:35.250 align:middle line:84%
think they were psychic
or talking to God,

00:07:35.250 --> 00:07:37.140 align:middle line:90%
or that their food was poisoned.

00:07:37.140 --> 00:07:38.970 align:middle line:84%
And so I began to
think that it was

00:07:38.970 --> 00:07:42.450 align:middle line:84%
dangerous and inappropriate to
use this ability in medicine,

00:07:42.450 --> 00:07:44.610 align:middle line:84%
because the only
example I saw were

00:07:44.610 --> 00:07:46.730 align:middle line:84%
these psychotic people
would come in, you know,

00:07:46.730 --> 00:07:49.890 align:middle line:84%
who may or may not have
been intuitive and psychic.

00:07:49.890 --> 00:07:51.300 align:middle line:90%
You know, it's a mixed bag.

00:07:51.300 --> 00:07:53.049 align:middle line:84%
You have to really
take a person's history

00:07:53.049 --> 00:07:54.670 align:middle line:90%
to find out what's going on.

00:07:54.670 --> 00:07:57.170 align:middle line:84%
So for 12 years, I went
the opposite direction,

00:07:57.170 --> 00:08:02.010 align:middle line:84%
and my UCLA training program was
very heavily biologically based

00:08:02.010 --> 00:08:04.530 align:middle line:84%
in that I learned how
to give out medication

00:08:04.530 --> 00:08:06.630 align:middle line:84%
and learned about
the neurochemicals

00:08:06.630 --> 00:08:09.510 align:middle line:84%
of human behavior, but very
little about anything else.

00:08:09.510 --> 00:08:11.380 align:middle line:90%
That was my training.

00:08:11.380 --> 00:08:13.410 align:middle line:84%
And it was fascinating,
but limited.

00:08:13.410 --> 00:08:14.520 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:08:14.520 --> 00:08:17.370 align:middle line:84%
Well let's talk about
psychosis for a moment.

00:08:17.370 --> 00:08:19.590 align:middle line:84%
Before we start going into
all the really juicy stuff

00:08:19.590 --> 00:08:22.350 align:middle line:84%
that you've been writing
about in recent years and now,

00:08:22.350 --> 00:08:23.350 align:middle line:90%
what about psychosis?

00:08:23.350 --> 00:08:25.290 align:middle line:84%
What did you begin to
understand over time?

00:08:25.290 --> 00:08:26.610 align:middle line:84%
Like you say, it's
a mixed bag, and you

00:08:26.610 --> 00:08:27.730 align:middle line:90%
go into personal history.

00:08:27.730 --> 00:08:29.460 align:middle line:84%
You'll see someone
ranting on the street,

00:08:29.460 --> 00:08:31.720 align:middle line:90%
someone's talking to them.

00:08:31.720 --> 00:08:33.150 align:middle line:84%
What do you have
to share with us,

00:08:33.150 --> 00:08:36.179 align:middle line:84%
because that seems to
be increasing in nature.

00:08:36.179 --> 00:08:38.970 align:middle line:84%
A lot more people, the
lines are blurring.

00:08:38.970 --> 00:08:41.190 align:middle line:84%
And is it because
veils are blurring,

00:08:41.190 --> 00:08:43.810 align:middle line:84%
or because the mind is
actually having its own shift

00:08:43.810 --> 00:08:44.610 align:middle line:90%
or breakdown?

00:08:44.610 --> 00:08:45.690 align:middle line:84%
What are you seeing
in that trend?

00:08:45.690 --> 00:08:46.480 align:middle line:90%
>> It depends.

00:08:46.480 --> 00:08:47.280 align:middle line:90%
It depends.

