00:41:35.630 --> 00:41:37.250 align:middle line:84%
the percentage of
thoughts that go

00:41:37.250 --> 00:41:38.750 align:middle line:84%
through their mind
that are negative

00:41:38.750 --> 00:41:40.370 align:middle line:90%
versus supportive and positive.

00:41:40.370 --> 00:41:42.480 align:middle line:84%
I mean, this is a chronic
condition of humanity,

00:41:42.480 --> 00:41:43.280 align:middle line:90%
isn't it?

00:41:43.280 --> 00:41:45.050 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, that's why we're here.

00:41:45.050 --> 00:41:49.280 align:middle line:84%
This is a very dark negative
place, along with the positive.

00:41:49.280 --> 00:41:53.600 align:middle line:84%
But once we learn how to
