00:41:53.600 --> 00:41:54.580 align:middle line:90%
energies--

00:41:54.580 --> 00:41:58.310 align:middle line:84%
now they're called emotions and
energies are the same thing--

00:41:58.310 --> 00:42:00.590 align:middle line:84%
we'll be able to be
