00:42:00.590 --> 00:42:02.270 align:middle line:90%
whatever comes our way.

00:42:02.270 --> 00:42:06.050 align:middle line:84%
And that's the point is
transformation, not denial.

00:42:06.050 --> 00:42:08.510 align:middle line:84%
