00:42:14.450 --> 00:42:15.560 align:middle line:90%
That's very powerful.

00:42:15.560 --> 00:42:18.350 align:middle line:90%
Doing it on a day by day basis.

00:42:18.350 --> 00:42:19.610 align:middle line:90%
then you could be free.

00:42:19.610 --> 00:42:22.340 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, you are
bogged down by all kinds

00:42:22.340 --> 00:42:23.720 align:middle line:84%
of negative thoughts
and feelings

00:42:23.720 --> 00:42:25.178 align:middle line:84%
that you don't know
what to do with

00:42:25.178 --> 00:42:27.140 align:middle line:90%
